{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180680/extras/cards.gif?t=1738356031\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Buckle up for a food truck deckbuilder where <strong>every ingredient has limitless potential</strong>. <br><br>Don't build just your deck \u2014 <strong>mutate your cards</strong> in surprising ways to discover game-breaking synergies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180680/extras/customers.gif?t=1738356031\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Sequence your plays</strong> to satisfy picky customers. <strong>Improve your truck</strong> with powerful, strategy-altering upgrades. <strong>Dazzle unique bosses</strong> and overcome challenges to earn coveted Nichelim Stars.<br><br>With <strong>hundreds of cards</strong> and <strong>dozens upon dozens of mid-game events and upgrades,</strong> no two runs are ever the same.<br><br>Served with a garnish of <strong>tasty tunes</strong> made to order by Josh Whelchel.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">For lovers of both culinary art and combinatorial explosion, the exciting world of curbside food sales awaits. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180680/extras/getcookin.gif?t=1738356031\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180680/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1738356031","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180680/page.bg.jpg?t=1738356031","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180680/05833d92617a169bd73cd12b767a8d3e4a5c8a54/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1738356031","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180680/05833d92617a169bd73cd12b767a8d3e4a5